main.name: Meik Kenworthy
main.bio: I'm a Software Engineer, Solutions Architect/Engineer at Immuta, & Founder of DDR.Live in Columbus, OH. My focuses are building communities and helping people to feel connected to one another, helping build tools and processes to better organize, and building tools and educating people on how to better protect themselves and their data..
